description:
This week is part two of Unqualified at San Diego Comic Con! First, Colton Haynes and Stephen Amell (ARROW) discuss set life and working together on Arrow, and advise Ashley, who wants to know if it’s weird that she hasn’t met her boyfriend’s friends and family after six years. Then, Anna and Sim are joined by Grant Gustin (THE FLASH), who talks about being a Comic Con veteran and Anna grills Grant and his fiancée LA Thoma about engagement details, their social media meet-cute, and wedding planning, and Tom Cavanagh (THE FLASH and ED) joins in to do a line reading and chat about officiating Grant’s and LA’s wedding. Finally, they call Rachel, who doesn’t know how to tell her close guy friend she doesn’t like him back.
